      "content": "i mean i appreciate the disclaimer but i'm really just trying to avoid a hypoglycemic episode overnight since i barely ate. if i skip the basal tonight, it shouldn't really matter because there's no food to process, right? it seems safer to just skip it than to risk a crash.",
