      "content": "but i already checked my levels and they're fine right now. the whole point of skipping is to prevent the drop from happening in the first place. if i take the insulin plus eat the snack you suggested, i'm basically just adding more insulin to my system when there's no actual meal to cover. wouldn't it be way more logical to just skip the dose entirely since there's no glucose entering my system from food? it seems like the more cautious thing to do.",
